    "name": "风暴之海",
    "steam_appid": 418180,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/e049e97d32e380373c78273a5e1b77d5.avif?t=1768395368\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名船长，你已经习惯了海风中咸腥味与寒冷潮湿，头顶上黑云笼罩的天空预示着风暴降至，远方的浓雾像厚重的帷幕隐匿了敌方的战舰，当你意识到危险时，敌人的船长已经下达了开炮的命令，一瞬间金属撞击声，尖叫，火炮的爆鸣声，“和谐的”交织在一起，随着就是船体的剧烈摇晃，水手们紧张地调整桅杆，迅速扭转船身炮手们全神贯注地装填弹药。决战一触即发，每一发炮火都是你命运的转折点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/a3faac497f69099ab8cc7f7322e05439.poster.avif?t=1768395368\" width=450 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/a3faac497f69099ab8cc7f7322e05439.webm?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/a3faac497f69099ab8cc7f7322e05439.mp4?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在火炮的轰鸣的回响中，两艘海盗船的桅杆交错在一起，随着你下达命令，水手们熟练的搭建起了登陆的木板，你将带头指挥冲锋，海盗战士们也挥舞着弯刀和火铳呐喊着登陆敌船，随着刀锋闪烁火铳爆鸣，甲板上充斥着鲜血与火药的气息，你将在浸透敌人鲜血的甲板上带领队伍突破敌人包围，赢得荣耀与财富！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/f205a027ee18272cde8eaff04ee1fe59.poster.avif?t=1768395368\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/f205a027ee18272cde8eaff04ee1fe59.webm?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/f205a027ee18272cde8eaff04ee1fe59.mp4?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/8860acf64336bc5766ac49c90fab762e.avif?t=1768395368\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的敌人们不会想到除了海面上的恶战，水下世界也暗流涌动，在《风暴之海》中你甚至可以召唤传说海怪克拉肯，利用它巨大的腕足缠绕敌方的战船拖入深海彻底摧毁它们。你也可以装备风化石，火焰石等神器驾驭大自然的力量召唤狂风，陨石等天灾作为打击敌人的利器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/c2451e8ea42507946c024f7a395bd982.poster.avif?t=1768395368\" width=458 height=268 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/c2451e8ea42507946c024f7a395bd982.webm?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/c2451e8ea42507946c024f7a395bd982.mp4?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/27fd4c6315ea6400c9c4410f8f957d12.avif?t=1768395368\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过战斗获得战利品无疑能“一夜暴富”，但稳定的“合法贸易”往来才能不让你的水手不饿肚子。在《风暴之海》中不只有珠宝，朗姆酒才是海上的硬通货，咖啡，丝绸，甚至炮弹，文物对海盗来说都是很好的免税商品，通过观察不同港口和黑市的商品差价，将货物转售到物资匮乏的城市，你会惊喜地发现，每一笔交易都能让你资产翻倍。毕竟，没有什么比赚取更多金币更能带来满足感了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/8f574e4357b9264b777da3346ba04cee.poster.avif?t=1768395368\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/8f574e4357b9264b777da3346ba04cee.webm?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/8f574e4357b9264b777da3346ba04cee.mp4?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/e195b8dea730f087dfc2b0f1ec7ba81b.avif?t=1768395368\" width=616 height=144 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《风暴之海》中你将化身“哥伦布”带领你的海盗船探索那些航海日志上的未知区域，你会发现每航行几个海里你就遭遇到一个全新的随机事件，保护商船，通过协助神秘流亡者揭开传奇海盗的神秘往事，挖掘在热带岛屿中被诅咒的宝藏击败护墓亡灵，三片神秘海域超大可探索空间，每片海域超过10个岛屿与百余个独立的冒险任务等你探索！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/a8cce8d43584c2f0429a1b872da19cdd.poster.avif?t=1768395368\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/a8cce8d43584c2f0429a1b872da19cdd.webm?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/418180/extras/a8cce8d43584c2f0429a1b872da19cdd.mp4?t=1768395368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
